name: SelfKey
description: SelfKey is a fast-growing DAO developing digital identity solutions. After Binance listed our first token, "KEY," the DAO is proposing a new token called SELF, which will be used for governance of the SelfKey DAO, and accompany the AI-powered digital identity system-the SelfKey iD. The accumulation of SELF is as a proof of reputation. To acquire SELF, users can lock their KEY tokens on their credentials and accumulate SELF ongoingly. Additionally, performing tasks in the DAO can earn users access to SELF minting. In the future, users can use SELF to mint their custom NFT, to acquire SELF ENS domain etc.
